@node plans "Future plans"

In current version mConfig does probably all it should do and it does it
good. But I still have some ideas to improve it:
· make mConfig some kind of complete configuration manager, with gui and
  other fountains.
· gather all modes (COPY, USE, SAVE) in MODE parameter.
· exchange RANDOM to RANDOM/M so all configuration names could written one
  after another, not separated with '|'

All ideas for improvements are welcome and I promise to implemet them (as
long as they are reasonable). Please send them to me.

@endnode


